{"type":"message","id":"74732812","parentId":"77035fee","timestamp":"2026-03-17T07:43:11.985Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问我是否可以访问飞书应用。这是一个测试问题，我应该直接回答。\n\n作为姚霖的助手，我确实有飞书工具的权限，可以在飞书中运行。让我简洁地回答这个问题。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"可以的 🦞\n\n我有完整的飞书工具权限，可以帮你：\n\n- 📅 查看/管理日程\n- 📁 读取/创建文档\n- 📊 操作多维表格\n- 💬 查看/搜索消息\n- 👤 查询员工信息\n- 以及更多...\n\n有什么需要我帮忙的？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":32746,"output":107,"cacheRead":2557,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":35410,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773733385207}}
