{"type":"message","id":"80a5c438","parentId":"4d89ac22","timestamp":"2026-03-17T07:44:23.793Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想查看\"工单管理系统\"里的订单。但我目前没有直接访问\"工单管理系统\"的工具。\n\n让我思考一下可能的解决方案：\n1. 工单管理系统可能是飞书的一个多维表格应用\n2. 可能是某个飞书文档\n3. 可能是其他系统\n\n我应该先搜索一下是否有相关的多维表格或文档。让我用 feishu_search_doc_wiki 搜索一下\"工单\"相关的内容，或者用 feishu_bitable_app 列出多维表格。\n\n先尝试搜索一下工单相关的文档/多维表格。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n我来帮你搜一下工单管理系统相关的内容。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_7zatf0yn0mxe_1","name":"feishu_search_doc_wiki","arguments":{"action":"search","query":"工单管理系统"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":565,"output":171,"cacheRead":35069,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":35805,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773733458512}}
