{"type":"message","id":"46cc230d","parentId":"9799a752","timestamp":"2026-03-17T13:11:40.510Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户说不需要用他的手机号，因为他们都知道（即联系人知道他的号码）。这意味着在回复模板中不需要提及具体电话号码，只需要说\"可以打电话\"就行。\n\n明白了，我更新一下 HEARTBEAT.md 中的回复模板。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"明白了！对方知道你电话，只需要说\"着急可以打电话\"就行。\n\n我更新一下模板：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_qido9ohm9ban_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md","newText":"- AI回复模板：「您好，我是姚霖的AI助手。他现在比较忙，您的消息我已收到。着急的话可以打电话给他」","oldString":"- AI回复模板：「您好，我是姚霖的AI助手。他现在比较忙，您的消息我已收到。着急的话可以拨打他的电话：XXX」"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":4743,"output":186,"cacheRead":43261,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":48190,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773753093317}}
