pnn3b"},"summary_highlighted":"...源GLM-4.7<h>大模型</h>：编程能力登顶SOTA，支持FP8轻量化部署](  资金将用于Claude<h>大模型</h>迭代及企业级安全工具研发，预计2...","title_highlighted":"seedance"}],"page_token":"{\"Mode\":0,\"GeoStrategyInfos\":{\"eu_nc\":{\"Mode\":0,\"Size\":20,\"Offset\":8,\"PreviousOffset\":0,\"Total\":8,\"strategies_infos\":[{\"strategies\":{},\"before_current_strategy_have_recalled_count\":0},{\"strategies\":{},\"before_current_strategy_have_recalled_count\":8}],\"last_strategy_infos\":{\"strategies\":{},\"before_current_strategy_have_recalled_count\":0},\"search_cold\":true}},\"size\":20,\"offset\":8,\"total\":8,\"shown_recordids_cache_Key\":\"7133889645745618945_790d9565-319c-401d-a813-c4563436e686_1773761030624977529\",\"search_cold\":true}"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773761030672}}
