{"type":"message","id":"e7aa1cb3","parentId":"75ba6017","timestamp":"2026-03-17T15:24:42.059Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"让我查看模型提供商的文档。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_twh3lv1wqkqw_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat /usr/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/providers/models.md 2>/dev/null | head -200"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":2544,"output":53,"cacheRead":54013,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":56610,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773761076490}}
{"type":"message","id":"b17f2bd5","parentId":"e7aa1cb3","timestamp":"2026-03-17T15:24:42.093Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_twh3lv1wqkqw_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nsummary: \"Model providers (LLMs) supported by OpenClaw\"\nread_when:\n  - You want to choose a model provider\n  - You want quick setup examples for LLM auth + model selection\ntitle: \"Model Provider Quickstart\"\n---\n\n# Model Providers\n\nOpenClaw can use many LLM providers. Pick one, authenticate, then set the default\nmodel as `provider/model`.\n\n## Quick start (two steps)\n\n1. Authenticate with the provider (usually via `openclaw onboard`).\n2. Set the default model:\n\n```json5\n{\n  agents: { defaults: { model: { primary: \"anthropic/claude-opus-4-6\" } } },\n}\n```\n\n## Supported providers (starter set)\n\n- [OpenAI (API + Codex)](/providers/openai)\n- [Anthropic (API + Claude Code CLI)](/providers/anthropic)\n- [OpenRouter](/providers/openrouter)\n- [Vercel AI Gateway](/providers/vercel-ai-gateway)\n- [Cloudflare AI Gateway](/providers/cloudflare-ai-gateway)\n- [Moonshot AI (Kimi + Kimi Coding)](/providers/moonshot)\n- [Mistral](/providers/mistral)\n- [Synthetic](/providers/synthetic)\n- [OpenCode Zen](/providers/opencode)\n- [Z.AI](/providers/zai)\n- [GLM models](/providers/glm)\n- [MiniMax](/providers/minimax)\n- [Venice (Venice AI)](/providers/venice)\n- [Amazon Bedrock](/providers/bedrock)\n- [Qianfan](/providers/qianfan)\n\nFor the full provider catalog (xAI, Groq, Mistral, etc.) and advanced configuration,\nsee [Model providers](/concepts/model-providers)."}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":13,"aggregated":"---\nsummary: \"Model providers (LLMs) supported by OpenClaw\"\nread_when:\n  - You want to choose a model provider\n  - You want quick setup examples for LLM auth + model selection\ntitle: \"Model Provider Quickstart\"\n---\n\n# Model Providers\n\nOpenClaw can use many LLM providers. Pick one, authenticate, then set the default\nmodel as `provider/model`.\n\n## Quick start (two steps)\n\n1. Authenticate with the provider (usually via `openclaw onboard`).\n2. Set the default model:\n\n```json5\n{\n  agents: { defaults: { model: { primary: \"anthropic/claude-opus-4-6\" } } },\n}\n```\n\n## Supported providers (starter set)\n\n- [OpenAI (API + Codex)](/providers/openai)\n- [Anthropic (API + Claude Code CLI)](/providers/anthropic)\n- [OpenRouter](/providers/openrouter)\n- [Vercel AI Gateway](/providers/vercel-ai-gateway)\n- [Cloudflare AI Gateway](/providers/cloudflare-ai-gateway)\n- [Moonshot AI (Kimi + Kimi Coding)](/providers/moonshot)\n- [Mistral](/providers/mistral)\n- [Synthetic](/providers/synthetic)\n- [OpenCode Zen](/providers/opencode)\n- [Z.AI](/providers/zai)\n- [GLM models](/providers/glm)\n- [MiniMax](/providers/minimax)\n- [Venice (Venice AI)](/providers/venice)\n- [Amazon Bedrock](/providers/bedrock)\n- [Qianfan](/providers/qianfan)\n\nFor the full provider catalog (xAI, Groq, Mistral, etc.) and advanced configuration,\nsee [Model providers](/concepts/model-providers).","cwd":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773761082076}}
{"type":"message","id":"7a081091","parentId":"b17f2bd5","timestamp":"2026-03-17T15:24:49.957Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，我现在知道 OpenClaw 支持哪些模型了。让我给用户一个总结。不过关于费用，这些是用户需要自己配置 API 的，妙搭这边可能有不同的计费方式。让我给用户列出支持的模型提供商。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"根据 OpenClaw 文档，支持的模型提供商如下：\n\n| 提供商 | 支持的模型系列 | 费用 |\n|--------|--------------|------|\n| **OpenAI** | GPT-4o, GPT-4.5, Codex 等 | 自己充值 API |\n| **Anthropic** | Claude Sonnet, Opus, Haiku 等 | 自己充值 API |\n| **Moonshot** | Kimi, Kimi Coding | 自己充值 API |\n| **GLM** | 智谱 GLM 系列 | 自己充值 API |\n| **MiniMax** | MiniMax 系列 | 自己充值 API |\n| **OpenRouter** | 聚合多种模型 | 自己充值 |\n| **Vercel/CF Gateway** | 聚合多种模型 | 自己充值 |\n| **Miaoda** | 当前使用 | 妙搭内置 |\n\n---\n\n### 💡 说明\n- **Miaoda（当前）**：免费，妙搭内置\n- **其他模型**：需要你自己提供 API Key，按各平台标准收费\n\n你想换成哪个？需要我帮你配置吗？🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":677,"output":269,"cacheRead":56317,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":57263,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773761082091}}
{"type":"message","id":"e1a34fdc","parentId":"7a081091","timestamp":"2026-03-17T15:25:34.677Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-17 23:25:34 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM | 姚霖 (ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b) [msg:om_x100b54a36811e4a4c3a5d71efa3dec7]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54a36811e4a4c3a5d71efa3dec7\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b\",\n  \"sender\": \"姚霖\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-03-17 23:25 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"姚霖 (ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b\",\n  \"name\": \"姚霖\"\n}\n```\n\n还有哪些免费的吗，可以用豆包吗"}],"timestamp":1773761134674}}
{"type":"message","id":"4d2c5d3c","parentId":"e1a34fdc","timestamp":"2026-03-17T15:25:58.912Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问还有哪些免费的模型，想用豆包。根据之前的搜索结果，豆包（Doubao）是字节跳动火山引擎的大模型，可以通过火山引擎接入。让我搜索一下 OpenClaw 是否支持豆包以及如何配置。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_fp20ys8vtbbw_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -r \"doubao\\|豆包\\|volcengine\\|ark\" /usr/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/providers/ 2>/dev/null | head -20"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":6675,"output":106,"cacheRead":50685,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":57466,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773761134675}}
