{"type":"message","id":"41a40b58","parentId":"b8bafc81","timestamp":"2026-03-17T15:26:02.505Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_1k23xbn90xgo_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"anthropic.md\nbedrock.md\nclaude-max-api-proxy.md\ncloudflare-ai-gateway.md\ndeepgram.md\ngithub-copilot.md\nglm.md\nhuggingface.md\nindex.md\nkilocode.md\nlitellm.md\nminimax.md\nmistral.md\nmodels.md\nmoonshot.md\nnvidia.md\nollama.md\nopenai.md\nopencode.md\nopenrouter.md\nqianfan.md\nqwen.md\nsynthetic.md\ntogether.md\nvenice.md\nvercel-ai-gateway.md\nvllm.md\nxiaomi.md\nzai.md"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":6,"aggregated":"anthropic.md\nbedrock.md\nclaude-max-api-proxy.md\ncloudflare-ai-gateway.md\ndeepgram.md\ngithub-copilot.md\nglm.md\nhuggingface.md\nindex.md\nkilocode.md\nlitellm.md\nminimax.md\nmistral.md\nmodels.md\nmoonshot.md\nnvidia.md\nollama.md\nopenai.md\nopencode.md\nopenrouter.md\nqianfan.md\nqwen.md\nsynthetic.md\ntogether.md\nvenice.md\nvercel-ai-gateway.md\nvllm.md\nxiaomi.md\nzai.md","cwd":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773761162499}}
{"type":"message","id":"21d03c3b","parentId":"41a40b58","timestamp":"2026-03-17T15:26:09.531Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"没有看到豆包/火山引擎的文档。让我检查一下 qianfan（百度千帆）是否支持豆包，或者看看有没有其他免费的可能。\n\n实际上，妙搭（Miaoda）本身就是字节跳动的产品，可能内置了豆包。让我直接告诉用户当前的情况。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"目前 OpenClaw 支持的免费/内置模型有限：\n\n| 模型 | 费用 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|\n| **Miaoda** ✅ | 免费 | 当前使用，妙搭内置 |\n| **Ollama** | 免费 | 本地部署，需自己安装 |\n| **HuggingFace** | 免费 | 有免费额度 |\n\n---\n\n### 关于豆包\n豆包是字节跳动火山引擎的模型，OpenClaw 目前**没有直接内置**。但妙搭本身就是字节跳动的产品，可能后续会接入。\n\n**建议**：先继续用 Miaoda，它是免费且稳定的。如果后续需要更强大的模型，可以考虑：\n\n1. 接入 Kimi（Moonshot）- 有免费额度\n2. 自己部署 Ollama - 完全免费\n\n要现在换成 Kimi 试试吗？🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":264,"output":231,"cacheRead":57597,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":58092,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773761162504}}
{"type":"message","id":"43d18113","parentId":"21d03c3b","timestamp":"2026-03-17T15:26:53.187Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-17 23:26:52 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM | 姚霖 (ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b) [msg:om_x100b54a365090ca4c37b64616f8025e]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54a365090ca4c37b64616f8025e\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b\",\n  \"sender\": \"姚霖\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-03-17 23:26 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"姚霖 (ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b\",\n  \"name\": \"姚霖\"\n}\n```\n\n好的，试一试吧"}],"timestamp":1773761213183}}
{"type":"message","id":"fe4a325d","parentId":"43d18113","timestamp":"2026-03-17T15:27:11.858Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想试试 Kimi (Moonshot) 模型。我需要帮助用户配置 Kimi 模型。\n\n首先我需要了解如何配置 Kimi 模型。让我查看一下 Moonshot 的文档。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_8gz3hg6miv6h_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat /usr/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/providers/moonshot.md | head -80"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":880,"output":82,"cacheRead":57341,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":58303,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773761213184}}
{"type":"message","id":"180d5c0b","parentId":"fe4a325d","timestamp":"2026-03-17T15:27:11.873Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_8gz3hg6miv6h_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nsummary: \"Configure Moonshot K2 vs Kimi Coding (separate providers + keys)\"\nread_when:\n  - You want Moonshot K2 (Moonshot Open Platform) vs Kimi Coding setup\n  - You need to understand separate endpoints, keys, and model refs\n  - You want copy/paste config for either provider\ntitle: \"Moonshot AI\"\n---\n\n# Moonshot AI (Kimi)\n\nMoonshot provides the Kimi API with OpenAI-compatible endpoints. Configure the\nprovider and set the default model to `moonshot/kimi-k2.5`, or use\nKimi Coding with `kimi-coding/k2p5`.\n\nCurrent Kimi K2 model IDs:\n\n<!-- markdownlint-disable MD037 -->\n\n{/_ moonshot-kimi-k2-ids:start _/ && null}\n\n<!-- markdownlint-enable MD037 -->\n\n- `kimi-k2.5`\n- `kimi-k2-0905-preview`\n- `kimi-k2-turbo-preview`\n- `kimi-k2-thinking`\n- `kimi-k2-thinking-turbo`\n  <!-- markdownlint-disable MD037 -->\n  {/_ moonshot-kimi-k2-ids:end _/ && null}\n  <!-- markdownlint-enable MD037 -->\n\n```bash\nopenclaw onboard --auth-choice moonshot-api-key\n```\n\nKimi Coding:\n\n```bash\nopenclaw onboard --auth-choice kimi-code-api-key\n```\n\nNote: Moonshot and Kimi Coding are separate providers. Keys are not interchangeable, endpoints differ, and model refs differ (Moonshot uses `moonshot/...`, Kimi Coding uses `kimi-coding/...`).\n\n## Config snippet (Moonshot API)\n\n```json5\n{\n  env: { MOONSHOT_API_KEY: \"sk-...\" },\n  agents: {\n    defaults: {\n      model: { primary: \"moonshot/kimi-k2.5\" },\n      models: {\n        // moonshot-kimi-k2-aliases:start\n        \"moonshot/kimi-k2.5\": { alias: \"Kimi K2.5\" },\n        \"moonshot/kimi-k2-0905-preview\": { alias: \"Kimi K2\" },\n        \"moonshot/kimi-k2-turbo-preview\": { alias: \"Kimi K2 Turbo\" },\n        \"moonshot/kimi-k2-thinking\": { alias: \"Kimi K2 Thinking\" },\n        \"moonshot/kimi-k2-thinking-turbo\": { alias: \"Kimi K2 Thinking Turbo\" },\n        // moonshot-kimi-k2-aliases:end\n      },\n    },\n  },\n  models: {\n    mode: \"merge\",\n    providers: {\n      moonshot: {\n        baseUrl: \"https://api.moonshot.ai/v1\",\n        apiKey: \"${MOONSHOT_API_KEY}\",\n        api: \"openai-completions\",\n        models: [\n          // moonshot-kimi-k2-models:start\n          {\n            id: \"kimi-k2.5\",\n            name: \"Kimi K2.5\",\n            reasoning: false,\n            input: [\"text\"],\n            cost: { input: 0, output: 0, cacheRead: 0, cacheWrite: 0 },\n            contextWindow: 256000,\n            maxTokens: 8192,"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":8,"aggregated":"---\nsummary: \"Configure Moonshot K2 vs Kimi Coding (separate providers + keys)\"\nread_when:\n  - You want Moonshot K2 (Moonshot Open Platform) vs Kimi Coding setup\n  - You need to understand separate endpoints, keys, and model refs\n  - You want copy/paste config for either provider\ntitle: \"Moonshot AI\"\n---\n\n# Moonshot AI (Kimi)\n\nMoonshot provides the Kimi API with OpenAI-compatible endpoints. Configure the\nprovider and set the default model to `moonshot/kimi-k2.5`, or use\nKimi Coding with `kimi-coding/k2p5`.\n\nCurrent Kimi K2 model IDs:\n\n<!-- markdownlint-disable MD037 -->\n\n{/_ moonshot-kimi-k2-ids:start _/ && null}\n\n<!-- markdownlint-enable MD037 -->\n\n- `kimi-k2.5`\n- `kimi-k2-0905-preview`\n- `kimi-k2-turbo-preview`\n- `kimi-k2-thinking`\n- `kimi-k2-thinking-turbo`\n  <!-- markdownlint-disable MD037 -->\n  {/_ moonshot-kimi-k2-ids:end _/ && null}\n  <!-- markdownlint-enable MD037 -->\n\n```bash\nopenclaw onboard --auth-choice moonshot-api-key\n```\n\nKimi Coding:\n\n```bash\nopenclaw onboard --auth-choice kimi-code-api-key\n```\n\nNote: Moonshot and Kimi Coding are separate providers. Keys are not interchangeable, endpoints differ, and model refs differ (Moonshot uses `moonshot/...`, Kimi Coding uses `kimi-coding/...`).\n\n## Config snippet (Moonshot API)\n\n```json5\n{\n  env: { MOONSHOT_API_KEY: \"sk-...\" },\n  agents: {\n    defaults: {\n      model: { primary: \"moonshot/kimi-k2.5\" },\n      models: {\n        // moonshot-kimi-k2-aliases:start\n        \"moonshot/kimi-k2.5\": { alias: \"Kimi K2.5\" },\n        \"moonshot/kimi-k2-0905-preview\": { alias: \"Kimi K2\" },\n        \"moonshot/kimi-k2-turbo-preview\": { alias: \"Kimi K2 Turbo\" },\n        \"moonshot/kimi-k2-thinking\": { alias: \"Kimi K2 Thinking\" },\n        \"moonshot/kimi-k2-thinking-turbo\": { alias: \"Kimi K2 Thinking Turbo\" },\n        // moonshot-kimi-k2-aliases:end\n      },\n    },\n  },\n  models: {\n    mode: \"merge\",\n    providers: {\n      moonshot: {\n        baseUrl: \"https://api.moonshot.ai/v1\",\n        apiKey: \"${MOONSHOT_API_KEY}\",\n        api: \"openai-completions\",\n        models: [\n          // moonshot-kimi-k2-models:start\n          {\n            id: \"kimi-k2.5\",\n            name: \"Kimi K2.5\",\n            reasoning: false,\n            input: [\"text\"],\n            cost: { input: 0, output: 0, cacheRead: 0, cacheWrite: 0 },\n            contextWindow: 256000,\n            maxTokens: 8192,","cwd":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773761231869}}
