{"type":"message","id":"39e723e3","parentId":"d5087c49","timestamp":"2026-03-17T15:27:25.612Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我看到当前配置是 Miaoda 模型。用户想换成 Kimi (Moonshot)，需要提供 Moonshot API Key。\n\n让我问用户是否有 Moonshot API Key，或者我需要帮他配置。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"当前用的是 Miaoda。要换成 Kimi，需要配置 **Moonshot API Key**。\n\n你有 Moonshot（Kimi）的 API Key 吗？\n\n- **有 Key**：我帮你配置\n- **没有 Key**：需要去 [Moonshot 开放平台](https://platform.moonshot.cn/) 注册获取\n\n🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":896,"output":113,"cacheRead":59133,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":60142,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773761241778}}
{"type":"message","id":"009b4e0f","parentId":"39e723e3","timestamp":"2026-03-17T15:28:00.325Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-17 23:27:59 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM | 姚霖 (ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b) [msg:om_x100b54a3613b3ca4c4f63ee471f4d35]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54a3613b3ca4c4f63ee471f4d35\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b\",\n  \"sender\": \"姚霖\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-03-17 23:27 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"姚霖 (ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b\",\n  \"name\": \"姚霖\"\n}\n```\n\n更换了之后还占用我的飞书AI额度吗"}],"timestamp":1773761280321}}
{"type":"message","id":"3c437d09","parentId":"009b4e0f","timestamp":"2026-03-17T15:28:06.749Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问换成 Kimi 后是否还占用飞书 AI 额度。\n\n根据之前搜索到的信息，妙搭的计费是消耗飞书 AI 额度（点数），但那是针对妙搭内置的 Miaoda 模型。如果用户换成自己的 Moonshot API Key，那就是直接消耗 Moonshot 的额度，不再消耗飞书 AI 额度。\n\n让我确认一下这个理解是否正确。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"不占用！切换后：\n\n- **Miaoda（当前）**：消耗妙搭/飞书 AI 额度\n- **Kimi（切换后）**：消耗你 Moonshot API 的额度，不再占用飞书额度\n\n所以如果你有自己的 Moonshot Key，用自己的更划算 🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":2931,"output":145,"cacheRead":57341,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":60417,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773761280323}}
