\n[90m│[39m  [2mSecurity warning — please read.[22m                                                           [90m│[39m\r\n[90m│[39m  [2m[22m                                                                                          [90m│[39m\r\n[90m│[39m  [2mOpenClaw is a hobby project and still in beta. Expect sharp edges.[22m                        [90m│[39m\r\n[90m│[39m  [2mBy default, OpenClaw is a personal agent: one trusted operator boundary.[22m                  [90m│[39m\r\n[90m│[39m  [2mThis bot can read files and run actions if tools are enabled.[22m                             [90m│[39m\r\n[90m│[39m  [2mA bad prompt can trick it into doing unsafe things.[22m                                       [90m│[39m\r\n[90m│[39m  [2m[22m                                                                                          [90m│[39m\r\n[90m│[39m  [2mOpenClaw is not a hostile multi-tenant boundary by default.[22m                               [90m│[39m\r\n[90m│[39m  [2mIf multiple users can message one tool-enabled agent, they share that delegated tool[22m      [90m│[39m\r\n[90m│[39m  [2mauthority.[22m                                                                                [90m│[39m\r\n[90m│[39m  [2m[22m                                                                                          [90m│[39m\r\n[90m│[39m  [2mIf you’re not comfortable with security hardening and access control, don’t run[22m           [90m│[39m\r\n[90m│[39m  [2mOpenClaw.[22m                                                                                 [90m│[39m\r\n[90m│[39m  [2mAsk someone experienced to help before enabling tools or exposing it to the internet.[22m     [90m│[39m\r\n[90m│[39m  [2m[22m                                                                                          [90m│[39m\r\n[90m│[39m  [2mRecommended baseline:[22m                                                                     [90m│[39m\r\n[90m│[39m  [2m- Pairing/allowlists + mention gating.[22m                                                    [90m│[39m\r\n[90m│[39m  [2m- Multi-user/shared inbox: split trust boundaries (separate gateway/credentials, ideally[22m  [90m│[39m\r\n[90m│[39m  [2m  separate OS users/hosts).[22m                                                               [90m│[39m\r\n[90m│[39m  [2m- Sandbox + least-privilege tools.[22m                                                        [90m│[39m\r\n[90m│[39m  [2m- Shared inboxes: isolate DM sessions (`session.dmScope: per-channel-peer`) and keep[22m      [90m│[39m\r\n[90m│[39m  [2m  tool access minimal.[22m                                                                    [90m│[39m\r\n[90m│[39m  [2m- Keep secrets out of the agent’s reachable filesystem.[22m                                   [90m│[39m\r\n[90m│[39m  [2m- Use the strongest available model for any bot with tools or untrusted inboxes.[22m          [90m│[39m\r\n[90m│[39m  [2m[22m                                                                                          [90m│[39m\r\n[90m│[39m  [2mRun regularly:[22m                                                                            [90m│[39m\r\n[90m│[39m  [2mopenclaw security audit --deep[22m                                                            [90m│[39m\r\n[90m│[39m  [2mopenclaw security audit --fix[22m                                                             [90m│[39m\r\n[90m│[39m  [2m[22m                                                                                          [90m│[39m\r\n[90m│[39m  [2mMust read: https://docs.openclaw.ai/gateway/security[22m                                      [90m│[39m\r\n[90m│[39m                                                                                            [90m│[39m\r\n[90m├────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╯[39m\r\n[?25l[90m│[39m\r\n[36m◆[39m  [38;5;209mI understand this is personal-by-default and shared/multi-user use requires lock-down. Continue?[39m\r\n[36m│[39m  [2m○[22m [2mYes[22m [2m/[22m [32m●[39m No\r\n[36m└[39m\r\n[1A\r\n[?25h[999D[4A[1B[J[32m◇[39m  [38;5;209mI understand this is personal-by-default and shared/multi-user use requires lock-down. Continue?[39m\r\n[90m│[39m  [2mYes[22m\r\n[?25l[90m│[39m\r\n[36m◆[39m  [38;5;209mOnboarding mode[39m\r\n[36m│[39m  [32m●[39m QuickStart [2m([38;5;138mConfigure details later via openclaw configure.[39m)[22m\r\n[36m│[39m  [2m○[22m [2mManual[22m\r\n[36m└[39m\r\n","name":"cd /home/gem/workspace/agent","retryInMs":5000},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773763833199}}
