{"type":"message","id":"b9db3a9e","parentId":"df85b9cb","timestamp":"2026-03-17T18:02:22.694Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_3xo8c1pvzw5q_1","toolName":"feishu_fetch_doc","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\"error\":\"[VALIDATION:400] Unable to extract document ID from URL: https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/h-mivAS0azlkkkVi4HmzYA. Please provide a valid Feishu document URL (e.g., https://xxx.feishu.cn/docx/xxx) or directly provide the document token\\n💡 Suggestion: Please check if the input parameters meet the requirements\\n📍 Context: input=https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/h-mivAS0azlkkkVi4HmzYA\",\"log_id\":\"20260318020222AA90ED00011AC013267D\"}"}],"details":{"error":"[VALIDATION:400] Unable to extract document ID from URL: https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/h-mivAS0azlkkkVi4HmzYA. Please provide a valid Feishu document URL (e.g., https://xxx.feishu.cn/docx/xxx) or directly provide the document token\n💡 Suggestion: Please check if the input parameters meet the requirements\n📍 Context: input=https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/h-mivAS0azlkkkVi4HmzYA","log_id":"20260318020222AA90ED00011AC013267D"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773770542682}}
{"type":"message","id":"3aea0c5d","parentId":"b9db3a9e","timestamp":"2026-03-17T18:02:26.317Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"这是一个微信文章的链接，不是飞书文档。我需要用其他方式来获取这篇文章。让我尝试使用 miaoda-web-fetch skill 来抓取这个网页。","thinkingSignature":"c5aa885112a52a6419b31e5dd2df5dc55f5f0d1920a2abbd71090558eee036f0"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_kt7xnnrda9oc_1","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"~/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-fetch/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":117890,"output":71,"cacheRead":35046,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":153007,"cost":{"input":0.035366999999999996,"output":0.0000852,"cacheRead":0.00105138,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.036503579999999994}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773770542689}}
{"type":"message","id":"a7cea664","parentId":"3aea0c5d","timestamp":"2026-03-17T18:02:26.333Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_kt7xnnrda9oc_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-fetch\r\ndescription: \"Use when user needs to crawl or fetch a specific URL to extract/summarize its content. Provides necessary command usage instructions for fetching known URLs. 触发词：网页抓取, 抓取网页, 提取网页内容, web crawl, 爬取, fetch url, 总结网页, 抓取 URL, 读取网页\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_fetch\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Fetch\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` 抓取指定网页内容，由 AI 自动总结/提取。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--url` | 网页 URL | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary（见 miaoda-web-search skill）\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL（见 miaoda-web-search skill）→ web-crawl 提取详情\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 抓取指定 URL 并提取信息\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli web-crawl --url https://example.com/pricing\r\n\r\n# 搜索 → 深入抓取：先搜索找到目标 URL，再抓取提取详细信息\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli web-crawl --url <搜索结果中的URL>\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`（见 miaoda-web-search skill） |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773770546325}}
{"type":"message","id":"d2e77bf6","parentId":"a7cea664","timestamp":"2026-03-17T18:02:37.382Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，我需要用 miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl 来抓取这个微信文章。让我执行这个命令。","thinkingSignature":"a7375b1c1ca6dd9bdb29b162205f1c0bf13a4f8b682e282d2f6767598d5373d4"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_j5it84cv9hug_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl --url \"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/h-mivAS0azlkkkVi4HmzYA\" 2>&1","timeout":60}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":116473,"output":98,"cacheRead":35046,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":151617,"cost":{"input":0.0349419,"output":0.0001176,"cacheRead":0.00105138,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.03611088}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773770546331}}
{"type":"message","id":"6f4f3471","parentId":"d2e77bf6","timestamp":"2026-03-17T18:02:42.642Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_j5it84cv9hug_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Webpage summary:\n由于您没有提供具体的网页抓取内容，我无法直接总结或提取关键要点。请您提供需要分析的网页文本内容，我会帮您进行总结和关键信息提取。"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":5250,"aggregated":"Webpage summary:\n由于您没有提供具体的网页抓取内容，我无法直接总结或提取关键要点。请您提供需要分析的网页文本内容，我会帮您进行总结和关键信息提取。","cwd":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773770562635}}
{"type":"message","id":"628aa1dd","parentId":"6f4f3471","timestamp":"2026-03-17T18:02:47.539Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"抓取失败了，可能是微信需要特殊处理。让我尝试用搜索的方式或者其他方式。\n\n实际上，微信文章通常需要登录才能查看完整内容，可能无法直接抓取。我应该告诉用户这个情况，或者尝试其他方式。","thinkingSignature":"7ec4082b57c90639c7249dd246bc366edfa024f003c4383bed6f506358c1ac71"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_r577oa3t08az_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s -L \"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/h-mivAS0azlkkkVi4HmzYA\" 2>&1 | head -100","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":116625,"output":117,"cacheRead":35046,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":151788,"cost":{"input":0.0349875,"output":0.0001404,"cacheRead":0.00105138,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.036179279999999994}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773770562641}}
{"type":"message","id":"0b03ac0e","parentId":"628aa1dd","timestamp":"2026-03-17T18:02:47.830Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_r577oa3t08az_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n    <head>\n        <meta http-equiv=Content-Type content=\"text/html;charset=utf-8\">\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width,initial-scale=1.0,maximum-scale=1.0,user-scalable=0,viewport-fit=cover\">\n<meta name=\"color-scheme\" content=\"light dark\">\n<meta name=\"apple-mobile-web-app-capable\" content=\"yes\">\n<meta name=\"apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style\" content=\"black\">\n<meta name=\"format-detection\" content=\"telephone=no\">\n<link rel=\"shortcut icon\" type=\"image/x-icon\" href=\"//res.wx.qq.com/a/wx_fed/assets/res/NTI4MWU5.ico\">\n<link rel=\"mask-icon\" href=\"//res.wx.qq.com/a/wx_fed/assets/res/MjliNWVm.svg\" color=\"#4C4C4C\">\n<link rel=\"apple-touch-icon-precomposed\" href=\"//res.wx.qq.com/a/wx_fed/assets/res/OTE0YTAw.png\">\n\n        <title></title>\n        <script>\n        (() => {\n            \n            const ua = navigator.userAgent;\n            const noMobile = !(/(iPhone|iPad|iPod|iOS)/i.test(ua) || /Windows\\sPhone/i.test(ua) || /(Android)/i.test(ua));\n            setTimeout(() => {\n                noMobile && document.title === '' && (document.title = '微信公众平台');\n            }, 1000);\n        })();\n        </script>\n        \n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"//res.wx.qq.com/t/wx_fed/weui-source/res/2.5.14/weui.min.css\">\n\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"//res.wx.qq.com/mmbizwap/zh_CN/htmledition/style/page/secitptpage/verify7c9da3.css\" media=\"all\">\n<script type=\"text/javascript\">\n  \n</script>\n\n    </head>\n    <body class=\"zh_CN \" ontouchstart=\"\">\n         \n<div class=\"weui-msg\">\n  <div id=\"tips\" style=\"display:none;\" class=\"top_tips warning\"></div>\n        <div class=\"weui-msg__icon-area\">\n      <i class=\"weui-icon-info-circle weui-icon_msg\"></i>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"weui-msg__text-area pc-area\">\n        <h2 class=\"weui-msg__title\">环境异常</h2>\n        <p class=\"weui-msg__desc\">当前环境异常，完成验证后即可继续访问。</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"weui-msg__opr-area\">\n      <p class=\"weui-btn-area\">\n        <a class=\"weui-btn weui-btn_primary\" id=\"js_verify\">去验证</a>\n      </p>\n    </div>\n    </div>\n\n<script type=\"text/javascript\">\nvar PAGE_MID='mmbizwap:secitptpage/verify.html';\n</script>\n        \n        <style>body,.wx-root{--weui-BG-0:#ededed;--weui-BG-1:#f7f7f7;--weui-BG-2:#fff;--weui-BG-3:#f7f7f7;--weui-BG-4:#4c4c4c;--weui-BG-5:#fff;--weui-FG-0:rgba(0,0,0,0.9);--weui-FG-HALF:rgba(0,0,0,0.9);--weui-FG-1:rgba(0,0,0,0.5);--weui-FG-2:rgba(0,0,0,0.3);--weui-FG-3:rgba(0,0,0,0.1);--weui-FG-4:rgba(0,0,0,0.15);--weui-FG-5:rgba(0,0,0,0.05);--weui-RED:#fa5151;--weui-REDORANGE:#ff6146;--weui-ORANGE:#fa9d3b;--weui-YELLOW:#ffc300;--weui-GREEN:#91d300;--weui-LIGHTGREEN:#95ec69;--weui-BRAND:#07c160;--weui-BLUE:#10aeff;--weui-INDIGO:#1485ee;--weui-PURPLE:#6467f0;--weui-WHITE:#fff;--weui-LINK:#576b95;--weui-TEXTGREEN:#06ae56;--weui-FG:#000;--weui-BG:#fff;--weui-TAG-TEXT-RED:rgba(250,81,81,0.6);--weui-TAG-BACKGROUND-RED:rgba(250,81,81,0.1);--weui-TAG-TEXT-ORANGE:#fa9d3b;--weui-TAG-BACKGROUND-ORANGE:rgba(250,157,59,0.1);--weui-TAG-TEXT-GREEN:#06ae56;--weui-TAG-BACKGROUND-GREEN:rgba(6,174,86,0.1);--weui-TAG-TEXT-BLUE:#10aeff;--weui-TAG-BACKGROUND-BLUE:rgba(16,174,255,0.1);--weui-TAG-TEXT-BLACK:rgba(0,0,0,0.5);--weui-TAG-BACKGROUND-BLACK:rgba(0,0,0,0.05)}@media(prefers-color-scheme:dark){.wx-root:not([data-weui-theme='light']),body:not([data-weui-theme='light']){--weui-BG-0:#111;--weui-BG-1:#1e1e1e;--weui-BG-2:#191919;--weui-BG-3:#202020;--weui-BG-4:#404040;--weui-BG-5:#2c2c2c;--weui-FG-0:rgba(255,255,255,0.8);--weui-FG-HALF:rgba(255,255,255,0.6);--weui-FG-1:rgba(255,255,255,0.5);--weui-FG-2:rgba(255,255,255,0.3);--weui-FG-3:rgba(255,255,255,0.1);--weui-FG-4:rgba(255,255,25