{"type":"compaction","id":"110421b9","parentId":"385bf0a8","timestamp":"2026-03-17T18:04:30.844Z","summary":"## Goal\n1. 查看工单管理系统订单（确认为飞书自建应用）\n2. 设置未回复消息自动AI回复功能（超过5分钟未回复则自动回复）\n3. 将AI模型从Miaoda切换到MiniMax 2.5\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- API Key必须严格保密，禁止任何形式外泄\n- 切换后不再消耗飞书AI额度\n- 自动回复不需要用户确认，直接发送\n- 回复需标明是AI助手\n- 检查时间限制在8:00-22:00\n- 不需要提及用户手机号，联系人知道号码\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- [x] 搜索工单管理系统，确认为飞书自建应用（非多维表格）\n- [x] 配置自动回复功能：每30分钟检查未回复消息，超过5分钟自动以用户身份回复\n- [x] 获取MiniMax API Key并配置到系统\n- [x] 切换模型为MiniMax M2.5\n- [x] API Key已存储到本地文件：`/home/gem/workspace/.force/openclaw/minimax-api-key`\n- [x] 更新HEARTBEAT.md添加自动回复任务\n\n### In Progress\n- [ ] 自动回复功能待心跳触发执行\n\n### Blocked\n- 无\n\n## Key Decisions\n- **从Miaoda切换到MiniMax M2.5**：用户选择方式2（API Key），不再使用飞书AI额度\n- **自动回复流程**：直接发送，标明AI助手，不等用户确认\n\n## Next Steps\n1. 等待心跳触发执行自动回复检查\n2. MiniMax M2.5模型已生效\n\n## Critical Context\n- 用户ID: ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b\n- API Key文件路径: /home/gem/workspace/.force/openclaw/minimax-api-key\n- 配置文件: /home/gem/workspace/agent/openclaw.json\n- 心跳配置: /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md\n- 当前模型: minimax/MiniMax-M2.5\n- 未回复消息追踪: /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/data/unreplied_messages.json\n\n---\n\n**Turn Context (split turn):**\n\n## Decisions\n- Work record from 李文娅 (Li Wenya) in 营销部 (Marketing Department) was submitted\n- Daily work summary recorded showing completed tasks for the day\n- Using bitable data as proxy: Since direct API failed, deriving employee count from \"工作日报\" (work daily report) submissions by counting unique submitters\n\n## Open TODOs\n- None explicitly mentioned in the conversation\n\n## Constraints/Rules\n- (none)\n\n## Pending user asks\n- Get the employee count for the organization\n\n## Exact identifiers\n- User ID: `ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b` (姚霖)\n- Bitable app token: `H1v1bFO1AapHXPsnSIoceOzxn6f`\n- Bitable app name: `汇报统计【工作日报】2025-12-09`\n- Table ID: `tbljv4saV7q2F0XJ`\n- Table name: `汇报数据明细`\n- Message ID: `om_x100b54ad1395d